# Vouched contributors for this repository.
#
# Vouched users can open issues and pull requests without Vouch auto-closing them.
# Repository collaborators with write/maintain/admin access and bots are allowed
# automatically by the Vouch GitHub actions, so the repository owner does not need
# to be listed here.
#
# Maintainers can manage this file by commenting on an issue:
#   !vouch [@user] [reason]
#   !denounce [@user] [reason]
#   !unvouch [@user]
#
# Denounce a user by prefixing the handle with '-'.

josxa
